(33, 'You will hear from students who have been successful at school and those who have not.  They will share what has worked for them as well as the cost of making poor decisions about their education.  You will be expected to engage in conversation and share you thoughts so that everyone can play a role in creating a safe learning environment.  Here is your chance to be heard.  Engage your brain! Let''s learn!!!', 1193, 1, 217, 0, '2011-06-10 23:58:08'),
