(45, 'Today, those of us who weren''t sleeping watched more of the video &quot;earth 2100&quot;. It''s a little disheartening to know that the perilous trajectory of human society is so uninteresting to some.  Maybe we are doomed.', 70, 1, 263, 0, '2011-06-10 23:58:08'),
(46, 'We began the period by reviewing the multiple intelligence assignment and the resources available within Class Connect.  We discussed the big ideas and essential questions for the unit we''re beginning (The Notion of Motion) and began completing the Word Root table, which will be collected a day or two before the unit test.  We talked about how motion could be described and how motion is everywhere.  We also discussed one way to quantify motion...by measuring the speed of an object in motion (measure the distance an object traveled and divide that distance by the time that the object traveled).  We finished the period by reviewing the essential components of a scientific experiment, practicing filling out an experimental design diagram, and attempting to complete a diagram for the experiment we will begin tomorrow.', 70, 1, 261, 0, '2011-06-10 23:58:08'),
