(62, 89, 21, 0, 'I\\''m your teacher, Mrs. Bennett. This is my eigth year teaching, my fourth year at NCHS. I\\''m married to my best friend (13 years and counting), and we have a small herd of cats. I have one younger brother who lives in D.C. and my mom, who lives just up the block. I also have 6 nieces and nephews. I love to watch TV, read mystery novels, garden, and bicycle. I am happy to be your teacher this semester, and look forward to helping all get the most out of chemistry! Please let me know what I can do to help you. :-)<br>', '2009-07-11 08:19:10'),
(68, 89, 0, 67, 'The \\&quot;live chat\\&quot; is a great idea, and we are working on adding a live chat feature using something called \\&quot;chat box.\\&quot; Again, I think we will still want to do some meetings face-to-face, but we also want to make those meetings more efficient by getting a group consensus in advance on some items. Fall is our busy season, so we were up to two meetings a week at one point, and I know that was difficult for some of the board members last year.', '2009-08-15 08:51:33'),
(70, 89, 0, 69, 'The virtual meetings would be used to reduce the time you all need to meet face-to-face, especially during our peak times. We can always choose a face-to-face meeting as needed, and we will need to do a few of those to be sure. Thanks for the feedback!', '2009-08-16 15:10:52'),
(73, 8, 0, 67, 'We\\''ve partnered with TokBox (http://www.tokbox.com) to bring live video conferencing to Class-Connect. It will be one of the features bundled in with this big \\''3.0\\'' release...it will probably be here in 1-2 weeks, not 100% sure yet. I\\''m also unsure of how many people our video application will be able to hold at one time; I\\''m assuming it will be able to hold about 20 people but I\\''ll keep you guys posted :)', '2009-08-19 03:02:44'),
(75, 128, 0, 61, 'Hi, im your student Clayton Scott. This is my sophmore year and i took this class because i am good at math. I play football and basketball. I have a sister that is a senior here and my brother is a senior in college at IU. I plan to have a good time in class this year.', '2009-08-19 11:15:30'),
(76, 89, 0, 72, 'Neel,\r\nI absolutely agree that face-to-face meetings are important (and yes, we\\''ll have snacks!) since you can accomplish a great deal in real time. The virtual meetings are more of a compliment to live meetings, and would allow us to ponder points, gather information, etc.in advance  to make the live meetings more productive.', '2009-08-19 12:02:06'),
(77, 131, 21, 0, 'I am david, i have 5 people in my family, a younger brother and sister. I like sports, and hanging out with friends, i play lacrosse for a couple different teams including the club at central. I took chemistry to graduate and for the experience. my goal for this year is to get an A in this class.', '2009-08-19 12:58:41'),
(78, 136, 21, 0, 'im 16, my name is adriana camargo.i took this class because it seemed interesting and i needed a credit.<BR>', '2009-08-19 12:59:30'),
(79, 133, 0, 62, 'I am matt songaila i have one brother and two divorced parents all of my stepbrothers and stepsisters added up equal 5. I have 1 dog a white german shepard and 1 bird a parakeet. I wrestle at school and i race dirt bikes out of school. I took chemistry because i was told that a large portion of the act is chemistry because i originally wanted to do physics. I hope to get out of this class a understanding of the elements and how some things work.', '2009-08-19 12:59:36'),
(80, 134, 21, 0, 'My name is Mariana Aldaba, im 16 years old and have an older sister and a younger brother. my interests include hanging out with friends and gymnastics. im taking this class because it looks good for college and i needed another science credit<BR>', '2009-08-19 13:02:15'),
(81, 138, 21, 0, 'hello my name ariel a.k.a re-re &amp;&amp; im 16 yrs old from chicago il..i join dhis klass 2 qet a science credit.!<BR>', '2009-08-19 13:02:44'),
(82, 137, 21, 0, 'Hi I am Katrina, and I am a cheerleader for 7 years now on a competitive team. I have 3 brothers and 2 sisters in my family. I am a exciting person and am ready for this class, i heard it is hard but you do some cool labs. I am taking this class because i heard there is some chemistry on the ACT and it was recomended for me. <br>', '2009-08-19 13:03:58'),
(83, 139, 21, 0, 'I am Brittany. I am a cheerleader and i am taking this class for the credit. My favorite season is summer and band is Blink 182<BR>', '2009-08-19 13:05:48'),
(85, 145, 0, 61, 'My name is Janet Ng and I am a junior in NCHS. I live with my mom, dad and older sister who is a senior in U. of I. From what I know of, all my cousins are female except for one. I have a black cat name Baliey despite being somewhat superstitious. I love to read, go onliine and play videogames. I took this class to learn chemistry because I thought it will be fun to learn and maybe useful for the ACTS and for the future. I hope to be a elementray school teacher when I grow up.', '2009-08-19 14:40:53'),
(90, 151, 0, 61, 'I\\''m Emma Sutherland. I live with my mom and sister whos a sophmore at Purdue. I love to be outside. I also like to spend time with my firends. I have a cat named Milo and a dog named Jessie. I plan to have a good sememster in chemistry.', '2009-08-19 15:22:49'),
(91, 153, 0, 61, 'yo my name is Stacia i have been going to naperville central for about 2 years i moved from missouri, Kansas City the show me state! but i love watching t.v. playing piano,boxing,mma,golfing,singing,and dancing other then that i am a senior i am taking this class one for interest but mostly b/c i need the credit   thank you for reading this. :)', '2009-08-19 15:37:55'),
(93, 160, 0, 61, 'Hi, I\\''m Emma Lindley and I\\''m a sophomore. I have an older sister who is a senior at Naperville Central. I\\''m in the marching band, rotary club, and Theatre Central here at school. I love to hang out with my friends and family, sing, write, and sleep. I\\''m looking forward to this year at Central!', '2009-08-19 16:17:15'),
(95, 165, 0, 61, 'I\\''m one of your students, Andrew Meder.  I am the youngest in my family.  I have two older sisters, they are both in college.  I decided to take chemistry because I heard chemistry uses math so, thought I would have a better chance to get an A in chemistry rather than biology.', '2009-08-19 16:48:16'),
(97, 170, 0, 61, 'Hey I\\''m Emily, I am a junior this year and have an older sister who is a junior at NIU. I live with my mom and dad, my family has two dogs (Sandy &amp; Sublime). I am excited for this year because I\\''m done with geometry. I\\''m excited for chemistry because it seems like it will be fun to do the experiments and you seem like a really fun and well-liked teacher. My reason for taking this class is partially for the ACT\\''s and partially because I need the credit though as well. I think this year will be really enjoyable, thanks!', '2009-08-19 17:04:41'),
(101, 172, 0, 61, 'hey im allie bonfield. im a sophomore. i took chemistry because i heard it uses math and i thought i could do well in it. i have an older sister who is a senior and a younger sister in 6th grade. i love playing soccer and just being outdoors with friends.', '2009-08-19 17:20:51'),
(102, 171, 0, 61, 'Hi! My name is Tessa and I am a Junior this year. I have one brother and a dog named Bo. There are 4 of us and we all love sports. I play soccer for NCHS and I have tried every sport under the sun! I like to watch sports and play sports :0) I took Chemistry because I needed the credit and because my dad told me that it was a really fun class. I hope to learn new things that I didn\\''t know before about chemicals and how they work together. Chemistry seems like an interesting topic and I can\\''t wait to do all the cool labs that I heard about!', '2009-08-19 17:22:28'),
(103, 181, 0, 61, 'I\\''m Austin, I have a very large family consisting of 3 brothers (2 older 1 younger) 1 younger. I am a hands on learner. I took this course because it seemed much more fun than biology and I heard it we get less homework. I hope to do well this year.', '2009-08-19 17:51:37'),
(110, 130, 21, 0, 'Hi, im sara. I have a family of six and a 30 pound cat. I love summer and to be outside. I took chemistry because i think&nbsp; its an important class to take for college.<br>', '2009-08-19 18:55:03'),
(111, 198, 0, 61, 'My name is Jim Barry, i am a napervillian born and raised. My family moved here from Beverly when i was born. I have 4 older brothers, 3 are in college and one is out. I have zero pets. I play football basketball and baseball. I took chemistry because i thought it was decided for us by the school... but hey, that doesnt mean i cant learn to love it. I hope to gain the understanding of chemistry and not to fail. PEACE', '2009-08-19 18:58:40'),
(117, 202, 0, 60, 'Hey, I\\''m Nikki Marquez. I\\''m a junior, and took Biology last year. I have one older brother who graduated about 6 years ago, Mike. I have 2 dogs, and 6 cats. She just had babies. I love to hang out with my friends alot, and now I\\''m working alot, so that does take away time from that. I took chemistry because I love math, and heard it was a fun class. This year, I hope i learn something new.', '2009-08-19 19:53:18'),
(120, 208, 0, 61, 'My name is Dan Suarez. I\\''m a sophomore and I was born here in Naperville. I have an older brother who\\''s 18 and just graduated from NCHS. I have a dog, a bird, and I play football for Central. I chose chemistry because I need the credit and it looked interesting.', '2009-08-19 20:55:03'),
(123, 173, 0, 122, 'Hi im Jordan Lowry. I have lived in Naperville all my life and i was born at Good Samaritin Hospital. I have three older sisters Ashley, Chelsea, and Bailey who are all finished with college, and i have one older brother, Ross who is at his last year at college. All my siblings attended Naperville Central. I play basketball and volleyball and baseball. My parents are Richard and Alexis Lowry and my dad is the 2nd boss of a Great Lakes Dreadging company and my mom works for the YMCA and teaches swimming. I love to play sports and hang out with my friends in my free time, and i am looking forward to high school', '2009-08-20 06:57:48'),
(152, 205, 0, 61, 'Hi Mrs. Bennett, My name is larry spencer. I live in a family of 6 with 3 sisters who are all younger than me. I have a dog, a turtle, a rabbit, and two fish. My hobbies are running and baseball. I am on our schools cross country &amp; track teams and in the summer I play baseball for naperville. I took chemestry because I thought that it would be a funner class than biology. I am hopeing to learn some cool experiments.', '2009-08-20 17:08:39'),
(160, 203, 0, 61, 'Hi, im John Boyum. You were my Teacher last year for DES, which was my favorite class because all my other classes are dull and boring. I have one older sister and i live with my mom. I love to hang out with friends, watch movies and listen/ play music. i play guitar. im really excited for this year of chem!', '2009-08-23 19:07:46'),
(161, 118, 28, 0, '<P>Hello General Chemistry Students,</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>By now you know that I am Ms. Solona Hollis, your General Chemistry Teacher.&nbsp; This is my 12th year teaching and my 2nd year here at Starr\\''s Mill High School.&nbsp;&nbsp; I am excited to have each of you in my class and look forward to working with you this school year.&nbsp; Please do not hesitate to let me know how I can help you this school year.&nbsp; <BR></P>', '2009-08-24 10:26:03'),
