(166, 250, 30, 0, '<FONT face=verdana>Hey everyone! I\\''m Elizabeth Grant and I\\''m a Junior this year. My birthday is July 1. On most weekends I go to Auburn to visit my sister or to Lake Martin just to hang out. I love to wakeboard and tube, and I\\''m also a leader for Kindergarteners at Heritage Christian Church for their program called \\"Awana.\\" I hope you guys have a great day/week/whatever! =]<BR></FONT>', '2009-08-25 15:49:44'),
(167, 258, 29, 0, '<H3><FONT face=georgia color=#ff33cc size=2>Hey everyone. I\\''m Kailey. I\\''m a junior this year, and my birthday is June 17th, 1993. I would say that my biggest hobby is fashion design. I also love to perform, and was in Advanced Drama 1 last year, but this school year I decided to take art instead because I need to be able to sketch to get into a college with a good art department. Two summers ago I did the Summer Seminars at the Savanah College of Art and Design where I took the fashion course where we created our own outfits. It was a blast! I also work at J. Andrew\\''s Andrew\\''s Bridal and Formal right here in Peachtree City. It\\''s so much fun. It\\''s great experience for someone who plans on making a living in that industry. My favorite part of the job is selling the prom dresses and accessories during prom season. I\\''ve been to New York City a few times, but my mom is going to take me there sometime in October to visit the Fashion Institute of Technology and just see if that\\''s&nbsp; actually a city I could see myself living in. Yeah, that\\''s pretty much everything. Obviously I don\\''t play a sport, but I am a huge NY Yankees fan! :)</FONT><FONT face=georgia color=#ff33cc size=2><BR></H3></FONT>', '2009-08-25 17:34:08'),
(168, 290, 28, 0, '<P><BR>Thomas M</P>\r\n<P>10th grade</P>\r\n<P>april 15, 1994</P>\r\n<P>i play soccer</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>', '2009-08-27 12:56:51'),
(169, 293, 29, 0, '<P><FONT face=\\"comic sans ms\\" color=#006600 size=2>hi.</FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=\\"comic sans ms\\" size=4><FONT color=#006600><FONT size=2>My name is <FONT size=3><STRONG><U>Michael Grauvogl</U></STRONG>.</FONT> I am a sophmore. My birthday is July 20th 1993.&nbsp;I was born in St.&nbsp;Louis MI.&nbsp;&nbsp;I love soccer. I have played soccer since I was a kid. Also i love to swim. I was on the SMHS swim team last year and I had a blast! We won county and alot of the team got to go to state. Im really hoping that this year we will win county again. As for teams that i cheer for,&nbsp;I love <FONT color=#ff0033><FONT>Manchester</FONT> United</FONT>, <FONT color=#0000cc>New England PATS,</FONT> and the <FONT color=#ff0000>BOSTON RED SOXS</FONT>!!</FONT><FONT size=2>&nbsp;I plan to be an orthopedic surgeon when i grow up. I hope that i get to meat everyone in the class before the end of school....... </FONT></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT face=\\"Comic Sans MS\\" color=#006600 size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style=\\"MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px\\">\r\n<BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style=\\"MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px\\">\r\n<P><FONT style=\\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff\\" face=\\"Comic Sans MS\\" color=#006600 size=4>and my favorite color is green :)</FONT></P></BLOCKQUOTE></BLOCKQUOTE>\r\n<P><FONT face=\\"Comic Sans MS\\" size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </P>', '2009-08-27 13:14:11'),
