(610, 289, 49, 0, '<BR>The understanding of plasma is important to the communications field because of the disturbances of the power. Mr. Watts and Mr. Gekelman both create plasma machines. Understanding solar flares are important because the solar flares erupt and&nbsp;are flung out into space where they form the solar wind. They are also channeled into the poles by the natural concentration of field lines. When fossil fuels are depleted, one of the few alternatives for large scale power production is nuclear fusion.I feel that improved plasma knowledge is necessary to know because if something happens like a storm or anything like that, scientists could know exactly what is going on with the plasma and why its acting so strange. Basically, I think it is necessary because we can understand more about the plasma and solar flares&nbsp;and also understand what goes on throughout the atmosphere when plasma is involved.<SPAN class=smalltext><BR></SPAN>', '2009-09-28 13:44:59'),
(611, 276, 47, 0, '<span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" face=\\"georgia\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" color=\\"#000000\\">1. Understanding of plasma important to the communications field because if we can understand plasma, we can move&nbsp;satellites&nbsp;out of the way of plasma but&nbsp;in order&nbsp;to do this we need to know how plasma reacts so we can&nbsp;predict&nbsp;what it will do.</font></font></span><div><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" face=\\"georgia\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" color=\\"#000000\\"><br></font></font></span></div><div><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" face=\\"georgia\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" color=\\"#000000\\">2.&nbsp;</font></font></span><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"line-height: normal; \\"><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" face=\\"georgia\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" color=\\"#000000\\">Mr. Watts has a machine that he hopes will help us understand the characteristics pertaining to solar flares.&nbsp;Mr. Gekelman and his colleagues have tried generating striations and other more exotic plasma structures allowing us to understand the structure of plasma.</font></font></span></span></div><div><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"line-height: normal; \\"><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" face=\\"georgia\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" color=\\"#000000\\"><br></font></font></span></span></div><div><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"line-height: normal; \\"><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" face=\\"georgia\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" color=\\"#000000\\">3. U</font></font></span><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"line-height: 18px; \\"><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" face=\\"georgia\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" color=\\"#000000\\">nderstanding solar flares is very important because if we can find what causes&nbsp;solar flares and how to avoid them we can save millions of&nbsp;dollars.</font></font></span></span></span></div><div><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" face=\\"georgia\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" color=\\"#000000\\"><br></font></font></span></div><div><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"line-height: normal; \\"><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"line-height: 18px; \\"><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" face=\\"georgia\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" color=\\"#000000\\">4. &nbsp;Plasma can be used to produce energy in special power plants and that can be used to power homes.</font></font></span></span></span></div><div><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" face=\\"georgia\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" color=\\"#000000\\"><br></font></font></span></div><div><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" face=\\"georgia\\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" color=\\"#000000\\">5. I think that plasma knowledge is not necessary but it could&nbsp;potentially&nbsp;be a useful power supply, therefore i think that we should continue our research on plasma.</font></font></span></div>', '2009-09-28 13:58:51'),
(612, 344, 49, 0, 'The understanding of plasma is essential to the operation of\r\ncommunications. Plasma storms can knock of grids of power and destroy\r\nsatellites which make our communications operate. Mr. Watts and Mr.\r\nGekelman make contributions to the undestanding of plasma by figuring\r\nout how it behaves, also they created a machine which can produce and contain plasma. The more we understand the process of plasma the\r\nmore we are able to be able to apply it to our lives today.\r\nUnderstanding solar flares is important because it hurts our field of\r\ncommunications. Solar flares can&nbsp;wipe out satellite systems and bring\r\ndown power grids and if we understood them, then subsequently this\r\ncould be avoided. Also if we understood plasma then we could use it for\r\nenergy through&nbsp;nuclear fusion thus solving much of the energy crisis. Improving our knowledge of plasma is a necessary endevour. It makes up 99% of of universe and has possibilites to create engery and save money through the costly repair of satellites and power grids. If we discovered an efficient way to harness plasma to solve our energy crisis it would also create new markets and stimulate economic growth or perhaps ease international relations. If this article is correct, then the significance of plasma is large and we must adhere to what it may offer us.', '2009-09-28 14:30:27'),
