(636, 346, 48, 0, '<P>Soha Jasani</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>1. Understanding plasma in the communications field is impotant because Solar Winds, massive enjections of plasma,&nbsp;ruin satellite systems and power grids.</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>2. Mr. Watts in currently building a&nbsp;machine that illuminate the mechanisms underlying solar flares. Mr. Gekelman is trying to find a way in which plasma can be used as and alternative energy source after fossil fuel runs out.</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>3. &nbsp;Understand solar flares is important because they erupta&nbsp;and fling parcticles into&nbsp;space&nbsp;and cause solar winds</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>4. Once fossil fulel is depleted, learning how to control hot plasma can help make clean endless fusion.</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>5. Improved plasma knowledge is necessary because the way that fossil fuel is being used today it might not last after a hundered or so years and we need alternative energy solutions.<BR></P>', '2009-10-03 09:48:27'),
(637, 405, 51, 0, '1. Plasma is important to understand because when a solar flare erupts on the surface of the sun, it can wipe out our satellites<div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\">&nbsp;and bring down power grids.</div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"><br style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"></div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\">2. Both Mr. Watts and Mr. Gekelman have created machines that can contain and be used to study plasma .&nbsp;</div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"><br style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"></div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\">3. understanding solar flares are important because the more we understand about them the better chance we have of predicting&nbsp;</div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\">when they will occur. It is important to know when theses solar flares occur because if we know before hand we will have a better&nbsp;</div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\">chance of protecting our power grids and satellites.</div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"><br style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"></div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\">4. Plasma will be useful when fossil fuels are depleted because we could use it as an energy source through the process of nuclear fusion.</div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"><br style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"></div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\">5. I think yes it is important because we will need it when our current fuel sourse runs out. plasma is important to understand to protect</div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\">our satellites and our power grids. if we learn more about plasma and how to use it to our advantage then it could only help us, so i think</div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\">yes it is important we learn about plasma and learn more about it to help us in the future.</div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"><br style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"></div>', '2009-10-03 10:38:09');
