(712, 300, 58, 0, '<div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; text-align: center; \\"><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-size: small; \\">PICK-AN-ELEMENT&nbsp;</span><b style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-size: small; \\">Titanium</span></b><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-size: small; \\">&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; text-align: center; \\"><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-size: small; line-height: 19px; \\"><br style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"></span></div><div style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; text-align: left; \\"><font class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" color=\\"#000000\\" face=\\"Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\\" style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; line-height: normal; \\"><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The essay on TITANIUM was written by&nbsp;Thomas M. Connelly Jr.,&nbsp;a senior vice president and chief science and technology officer at DuPont. A chemical engineer by training, Connelly has been with DuPont since 1977 and has served as manager for a variety of DuPont businesses in the U.S., Europe, and Asia. Connelly says that \\"the chemistry of titanium is closely linked to the development of several modern industries that have improved the quality of our lives.\\" Titanium improves the performance of high-tech applications used in the military, such as the construction of planes, and the medical field, along with many other places, like underwater vessels that have to stand high pressures. It can also be used to replace damaged human bones, or as part of dental implants. Titanium is part of the transition elements and is in period 4, group 4. It is normally found as a solid and is a metal. Titanium is used in alloys and is as strong as steel, yet much lighter. It is not dangerous in normal exposure quantities. The actual metal we know as titanium, is not found in nature.&nbsp;</span><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Geneva, Swiss, SunSans-Regular; \\"><span class=\\"Apple-style-span\\" style=\\"font-size: small;\\">It comes primarily from ilmenite ore.</span></span></span></font></div>', '2009-10-06 20:04:59'),
