(2029, 1363, 168, 0, 'After watching the movie "earth 2100" I had a stronger understanding of the possible impacts that we could cause for future generations. It certainly was a wake up call as many classmates have stated, and I believe it is this generations&nbsp;responsibility&nbsp;to provide a better future for generations to come and not neglect and take for granted everything that the earth is&nbsp;providing&nbsp;for us now. There are still things that can be done to reduce the use of fossil fuels and lessen the dependency on resources that will eventually run out, and with more people helping out , this can be achieved. Even though what was shown in the movie was a worst case&nbsp;scenario, it can still happen with our&nbsp;neglect&nbsp;to change our life-style.&nbsp;', '2010-08-30 20:46:03'),
